- ✅ Real-time entropy visualization
- ✅ Crypto-secure random generation
- ✅ Copy to clipboard

### 2️⃣ Form Validation
- ✅ Required field validation (name, username, password)
- ✅ Real-time strength checking
- ✅ Visual error indicators (red borders)
